OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,FA former soldier present at an
OL,8,Fincident where three IRA men were
OL,9,Fkilled contended he fired "aimed
OL,10,Fshots" believing his colleagues were
OL,11,Fin danger.
OL,13,FThe veteran, known as Soldier F, has
OL,14,Frefused to testify in person at the
OL,15,Finquest into the deaths of Peter Ryan,
OL,16,FTony Doris and Lawrence McNally in
OL,17,FCoagh, Co Tyrone.
