OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,FThe men were intercepted on June 3
OL,8,F1991 in a stolen car by SAS soldiers
OL,9,Fwho believed they were intending to
OL,10,Fmurder a member of the security forces.
OL,12,FAll three were shot dead in a hail of
OL,13,Fgunfire. Previous inquest hearings
OL,14,Fwere told up to 150 rounds were fired.
OL,16,FMr Justice Michael Humphreys took
OL,17,Flegal action in a bid to secure
OL,18,FSoldier F's attendance at the inquest
OL,19,Finto the men's deaths.
