OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,FThe ex-soldier was recently sentenced
OL,8,Fto six months in prison in Scotland
OL,9,Ffor contempt of court for refusal to
OL,10,Fcomply with a subpoena to give
OL,11,Fevidence.
OL,13,FHis lawyers cited mental health issues
OL,14,Fin arguing why he should not be
OL,15,Fcompelled to give evidence.
OL,17,FThe proceedings in Scotland are
OL,18,Fsubject to an appeal that was listed
OL,19,Ffor April.
