OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,FAt a previous hearing of the inquest
OL,8,Fearlier this month, Mr Justice
OL,9,FHumphreys said the timescales involved
OL,10,Fmeant that the inquest would have to
OL,11,Fconclude without hearing from the
OL,12,Fveteran.
OL,14,FUnder the Government's Legacy Act,
OL,15,Flegacy inquests in Northern Ireland
OL,16,Fneed to conclude hearing evidence by a
OL,17,Fdeadline of May 1 this year.
OL,19,FThe bulk of evidence has already been
OL,20,Fheard in the Coagh inquest, apart from
OL,21,FSoldier F's testimony.
