OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,FThe former serviceman is not the same
OL,8,Fperson as the Soldier F who is facing
OL,9,Ftwo counts of murder over the shooting
OL,10,Fof 13 civil rights protesters in
OL,11,FLondonderry in 1972, an event known as
OL,12,FBloody Sunday.
OL,14,FAn inquest review hearing in Belfast
OL,15,Fon Friday heard a statement from
OL,16,FSoldier F.
OL,18,FThe evidence included police interview
OL,19,Fnotes dated June 5 1991 and a five-
OL,20,Fpage statement by Soldier F dated
OL,21,FNovember 10 2022.
