OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,FThe statement, which was read to the
OL,8,Fcourt, included Soldier F saying he
OL,9,Fhad "struggled with ill health for
OL,10,Fsome time" and with "recent
OL,11,Fbereavement issues", but said he had
OL,12,F"done his best to assist in this
OL,13,Finquest".
OL,15,FHe said he was a member of the special
OL,16,Fmilitary unit (SMU) involved in a
OL,17,Fplanned arrest operation in Coagh in
OL,18,FMay-June 1991.
