OL,7,FIt was described as being directed at
OL,8,Fterrorists believed to be targeting an
OL,9,Findividual who had a routine of
OL,10,Fsitting in a car park reading a
OL,11,Fnewspaper each morning.
OL,13,F"Our task was to effect an arrest if
OL,14,Fany terrorists turned up and attempted
OL,15,Fto kill the intended victim," Soldier
OL,16,FF said in the statement.
