OL,8,Fadvance for the location which was
OL,9,F"difficult to cover" as it could be
OL,10,Fapproached from several directions and
OL,11,Fwas a residential area.
OL,13,FIt was planned to conceal soldiers in
OL,14,Fan improvised Bedford truck.
