OL,7,FSoldier F said the operation took
OL,8,Fplace on May 31, and described wearing
OL,9,Fcivilian clothes but with a uniform in
OL,10,Fa bag to change into "so the
OL,11,Fterrorists would be in no doubt it was
OL,12,Fan Army arrest operation if we
OL,13,Fconfronted them".
OL,15,FBut on that day, the operation was
OL,16,Fstood down and the soldiers returned
OL,17,Fto base.
OL,19,FThey returned on June 3.
