OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,F"I can say it was a hard arrest
OL,8,Foperation with the use of lethal force
OL,9,Fonly as a last resort," Soldier F said
OL,10,Fin his statement.
OL,12,FAfter arriving in Coagh, Soldier F
OL,13,Fsaid he changed into military uniform.
OL,15,F"The first message I can recall coming
OL,16,Fover the radio were the words 'stand
OL,17,Fby, stand by', followed quickly by
OL,18,F'go, go, go'," he said.
