OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,F"I started running down the laneway to
OL,8,Fthe corner of the hotel. I can recall
OL,9,Fhearing shots being fired. I have no
OL,10,Fidea how many or what calibre but knew
OL,11,Fthis was an engagement with terrorists.
OL,13,F"I could see a car crashed into the
OL,14,Fwall at the side of the road
OL,15,Fapproximately 40-50 yards up the road.
OL,16,FI recall seeing two people inside the
OL,17,Fcar. One in the rear was pointing a
OL,18,Frifle in the direction of the lorry. I
OL,19,Fbelieve he was about to fire or was
OL,20,Fmaybe firing.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
