OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,F"After so long, all I can now say is
OL,8,Fthere was firing going on. I could not
OL,9,Fdistinguish between the noise of the
OL,10,Fshots. I felt the soldiers in the
OL,11,Florry were at risk so I fired aimed
OL,12,Fshots at the individual with the
OL,13,Frifle. I do not recall how many shots
OL,14,FI fired.
OL,16,F"This was the only location that I
OL,17,Ffired from.
OL,19,F"I did see another figure in the car
OL,20,Fin the front but my concentration was
OL,21,Fon the terrorist in the back.
