OL,3,CSoldier 'fired shots' to protect
OL,4,Ccolleagues, inquest into deaths of IRA
OL,5,Cmen told
OL,7,F"I cannot be certain whether I hit
OL,8,Fthat terrorist in the rear, but when I
OL,9,Flost sight of him I stopped firing. I
OL,10,Frecall that other SMU members were
OL,11,Fmoving forward. I can't say who fired
OL,12,F... this all took place in a matter of
OL,13,Fseconds.
OL,15,F"I heard soldiers shouting 'stop', and
OL,16,FI also shouted 'stop' meaning for
OL,17,Fanyone around me if still firing to
OL,18,Fstop. This is normal SOP (standard
OL,19,Foperating procedure).
