OL,7,F"At some point I recall seeing
OL,8,Fsubstance alight beneath the car and
OL,9,Fthe car went up very fast."
OL,11,FSoldier F also said there was no
OL,12,Fpreparation for being interviewed by
OL,13,Fpolice at the time.
OL,15,FThe inquest heard that this concluded
OL,16,Fthe evidence.
OL,18,FThe coroner said he would deliver
OL,19,Fprovisional findings in the case on
OL,20,FApril 11.
